OL,3,CJersey Opera House needs further #1.5
OL,4,Cmillion to open
OL,6,FThe company responsible for putting on
OL,7,Fshows at Jersey Opera House says an
OL,8,Fadditional #1.5 million is needed by
OL,9,FMarch for the venue to open.
OL,11,FJersey Opera House Limited says that
OL,12,F"essential technical infrastructure
OL,13,Fupgrades" are needed to ensure it can
OL,14,F"operate as a fully equipped theatre".
OL,16,FThe registered charity says upgrades
OL,17,Finclude a new prompt desk, performance
OL,18,Fcommunication systems, and the
OL,19,Fsupporting cabling infrastructure.
