OL,6,FIt adds that the productions it can
OL,7,Fstage will be "severely limited"
OL,8,Fwithout said upgrades.
OL,10,FThe situation threatens to delay the
OL,11,Fproposed opening night in the Autumn.
OL,13,FSpeaking to the island's government
OL,14,Flast week, ITV News was told the
OL,15,Fproject was #250,000 under budget, but
OL,16,Fthere was disagreement on who should
OL,17,Fpay for the outstanding extras.
