OL,3,CJersey Opera House needs further #1.5
OL,4,Cmillion to open
OL,6,FJersey Opera House Limited explain:
OL,7,F"As a registered charity, we rely on
OL,8,Fthe generosity of our supporters and
OL,9,Fhave taken the initiative to raise the
OL,10,Frequired monies.
OL,12,F"We have already raised over #1
OL,13,Fmillion towards these improvements
OL,14,Fthrough philanthropic donations, and
OL,15,Fwe seek to urgently raise a further
OL,16,F#1.5 million by the end of March to
OL,17,Fget this project over the line.
