OL,3,CJersey Opera House needs further #1.5
OL,4,Cmillion to open
OL,6,F"This will enable us to open and
OL,7,Fsustainably operate as we mean to go
OL,8,Fon with a first-class experience for
OL,9,Faudiences and participants.
OL,11,F"Without this funding, the range and
OL,12,Fquality of performances we can host
OL,13,Fwill be significantly limited,
OL,14,Faffecting both local and touring
OL,15,Fproductions."
OL,17,FSpeaking to ITV News last week, Deputy
OL,18,FKirsten Morel said that "from the
OL,19,Fbuilding perspective", the opera house
OL,20,Fwas completed.
