OL,3,CJersey Opera House needs further #1.5
OL,4,Cmillion to open
OL,6,FHowever, the Minister added: "There
OL,7,Fare still questions around the
OL,8,Ftechnology that's available in the
OL,9,FOpera House.
OL,11,F"The government and the public have
OL,12,Fput #12 million into this building, so
OL,13,FI think it is a case of looking for
OL,14,Fother forms of revenue.
OL,16,F"We want this building to be open as
OL,17,Fquickly as possible, so it is going to
OL,18,Fbe a trade-off of time over the work
OL,19,Fthat we do."
